Class DefaultAuto

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.firstinspires.ftc.teamcode.states.AbState
      • org.firstinspires.ftc.teamcode.states.DefaultAuto

  • public class DefaultAuto
extends AbState
    DefaultAuto when, ran iteratively, shoots rings at each powershot, moves the wobble goal to the necessary destination, and stops. This class uses MoveAndShoot, MoveToWobbleZone, and EndState.
    Author:
    Will (wrtc9)
